result.title: Techkriti's IOPC
result.content:
Hello !!!

IOPC is the annual International Online Programming Contest of IIT Kanpur,India, organized by the Techkriti team. Prizes worth 1,00,000 INR are at stake in this competition. We have tried to make the contest utilize the best of your time. The contest is a three hour contest and it will be held on 14th of March from 8-11 pm(IST). The link to the contest is- https://www.techgig.com/challenge/nyt7b517bpm34ar

REGISTER NOW

May the force be with you!
